framework_instructions:
- Next.js 15, Tailwind CSS v3, TypeScript strict.
- ALL colors via Tailwind hex arbitrary values (e.g. bg-[#0a0a0a]) — NEVER inline style={{ backgroundColor: ... }} for layout/sidebar/wrapper elements. NEVER named Tailwind colors (no bg-green-500).
- CANONICAL LAYOUT PATTERN — every page must use this exact structure:
  <div className="flex h-screen bg-[#0a0a0a] overflow-hidden">
    <aside className="w-[220px] flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col border-r border-[#1f1f1f] bg-[#0a0a0a] h-screen sticky top-0">
    <main className="flex-1 overflow-y-auto">
      <div className="sticky top-0 z-10 bg-[#0a0a0a]/80 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-[#1f1f1f] px-6 py-3 ...">
- CANONICAL SIDEBAR — brand (🦞 Pulse v2 / HBx AI Factory) + nav + footer (Schellie / Orchestrator · Online + green pulse dot). Active nav item: bg-[#1a1a1a] text-[#ededed]. Inactive: text-[#888] hover:text-[#ededed] hover:bg-[#111111].
- NAV ITEMS (always this exact array):
  { icon: "▤", label: "Overview", href: "/" }
  { icon: "⊡", label: "Agents", href: "#" }
  { icon: "✓", label: "Tasks", href: "#" }
  { icon: "⊕", label: "Leads", href: "/leads" }
  { icon: "⌂", label: "Communities", href: "/communities" }
  { icon: "◫", label: "Lots", href: "/lots" }
  { icon: "⊞", label: "Divisions", href: "/divisions" }
  { icon: "◷", label: "Calendar", href: "#" }
  { icon: "◉", label: "Notifications", href: "#" }
  { icon: "⚙", label: "Settings", href: "#" }
  { icon: "◈", label: "Status", href: "/status" }
- Server components fetch from Supabase via createClient(@supabase/supabase-js). Client components receive data as props — no fetch() inside client components.
- Use 'use client' only for interactive components. Export pages as export default function PageName() — NOT arrow functions.
- Only import packages in package.json. No new dependencies.
- TypeScript: no implicit any. Explicit types for all props and data.
